
Lucky is a game of double or nothing.  Just press the left mouse
button and you get fifty points.  When you click on start, the
wheel spins.  To see the winning combinations click on Plan.
When you win, the amount won shows up under your bank.  You then
have three choices, try and double the whole thing, bank 1/2 and
try to double the rest or bank the whole (1) amount.  You can
increase your bet before spinning from 1 to 10 point

A little strategy--if you have two in a row increase your chips
to ten before spinning the third time.  Three crowns at 10 is a
1000 points.  Good luck.   Steve Garee


